♪Let it be buried with past glory♪

25
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:52,820
♪If kindness is just a beautiful lie♪

26
00:01:53,260 --> 00:02:00,060
♪Then I shall keep wearing my disguise♪

27
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:18,780
=Lies Never Lie=

28
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,120
Meng Zhengyi,

29
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:25,529
why did you set up Zhiyuan
to send money to Bao Xijie?

30
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:26,880
Yifei,

31
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:27,489
try this.

32
00:02:27,490 --> 00:02:28,680
The wine tastes pretty good.

33
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:33,370
Ning Zhiyuan is all right, isn't he?

34
00:02:37,770 --> 00:02:39,769
I'm the deputy director
of Tianxiang Group.

35
00:02:39,770 --> 00:02:41,579
Everything I do is for the company

36
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:42,720
and for you.

37
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:44,739
The collaboration with the government

38
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,530
is currently at a crucial stage.

39
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:49,019
We must cut ties with
business partners drowning in debt,

40
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,840
like Bao Xijie.

41
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:52,530
The money had to be lent,

42
00:02:52,770 --> 00:02:54,770
but not from the company.

43
00:02:58,770 --> 00:03:00,370
Ning Zhiyuan is an outsider here,

44
00:03:00,980 --> 00:03:03,979
so using his name

45
00:03:03,980 --> 00:03:05,560
was the most appropriate way.

46
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,330
As for what happened to Bao Xijie,

47
00:03:07,490 --> 00:03:10,370
how could I have predicted he'd be there?

48
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:13,210
I don't care what you're up to,

49
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:14,929
but I'm warning you,

50
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:17,000
don't go behind my back
and mess up with Zhiyuan.

51
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:22,120
If he threatens the company's interests,

52
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:24,440
will you still choose him?

53
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,050
Yes,

54
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,880
I will.

55
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:30,049
Also, let me be clear.

56
00:03:30,050 --> 00:03:31,960
My bottom line is Ning Zhiyuan.

57
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:33,680
If you ever do this again,

58
00:03:35,530 --> 00:03:36,770
please leave.

59
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:43,959
=Lies Never Lie=
=Episode 8=

60
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:47,030
(Inpatient)

61
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,680
Let's end this.

62
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:05,440
Mochou, wake up.

63
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:09,330
Wake up now, Mochou.

64
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:58,819
Give some response.

65
00:04:58,820 --> 00:04:59,970
Say something.

66
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,289
One at a time.

67
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:02,370
One at a time.

68
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:04,640
Calm down. Let's do it one at a time.

69
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:06,729
I can't answer that right now.

70
00:05:06,730 --> 00:05:08,849
I'll let you know immediately
if there's any update.

71
00:05:08,850 --> 00:05:10,769
Is there any progress
on the hotel murder case?

72
00:05:10,770 --> 00:05:12,499
The case can't be disclosed.

73
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:15,089
The murder case from a few days ago
has drawn public attention.

74
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:16,499
Are there any updates on it?

75
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:19,050
We can't disclose anything regarding that.

76
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:20,729
Why are you discharged
from the hospital?

77
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:22,490
What's going on
outside the police station?

78
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,379
Li Guangrong is dead.

79
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:27,080
Don't use the main entrance.
Come with me.

80
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:32,440
Why is the entrance surrounded
by reporters?

81
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:36,619
The higher-ups wanted to
keep this case confidential,

82
00:05:36,620 --> 00:05:38,459
but somehow, the news leaked,

83
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:40,680
and now reporters from all media outlets
have flocked in.

84
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:43,610
Will external pressure

85
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:45,440
help speed up the process
of solving the case?

86
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:47,529
The higher-ups are
under tremendous pressure now.

87
00:05:47,530 --> 00:05:48,939
Chief Ou arrived early this morning

88
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,520
to oversee the case.

89
00:05:55,210 --> 00:05:57,730
You seem to pay extra attention
to Li Guangrong.

90
00:05:58,330 --> 00:06:00,490
What are you trying to
find out from him?

91
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:03,320
He almost killed me.

92
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:05,610
I just want to find out

93
00:06:06,410 --> 00:06:07,850
who was after me.

94
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:10,649
We found knives of various sizes

95
00:06:10,650 --> 00:06:12,930
from Li Guangrong's place.

96
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:14,259
Among them,

97
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:18,000
this one matches the weapon
used to kill Bao Xijie and his family.

98
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,499
According to Mochou's recollection,

99
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,640
Li Guangrong admitted
to killing Bao Xijie and his family.

100
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:28,000
Did he kill them
out of personal revenge?

101
00:06:28,140 --> 00:06:29,290
Or was he hired?

102
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:31,880
Whether or not it's a personal revenge,
we're still working on it.

103
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,459
But we did find
a bloodstained leather bag

104
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,059
at his place.

105
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:37,250
It contained one million in cash.

106
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:39,579
Forensics confirmed the blood
on the leather bag

107
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:40,939
belonged to Bao Xijie.

108
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:43,059
We also found a large number
of secretly taken photos

109
00:06:43,060 --> 00:06:44,850
of Bao Xijie.

110
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,579
We speculate

111
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:49,089
that Li Guangrong planned to murder

112
00:06:49,090 --> 00:06:50,729
Bao Xijie and his family

113
00:06:50,730 --> 00:06:52,880
and then take the money.

114
00:06:54,530 --> 00:06:55,259
In other words,

115
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,729
Bao Xijie hired him

116
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:58,139
but didn't pay as promised,

117
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:59,939
so the latter killed him

118
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:01,680
to set the rules.

119
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:05,170
Currently, all the evidence supports
this theory.

120
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:08,899
But there are many restaurants
in Baizhou.

121
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:11,409
How could he be sure that Bao Xijie

122
00:07:11,410 --> 00:07:13,640
would be at Haitian Grand Hotel
celebrating his birthday?

123
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:15,209
Chief Ou,

124
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:17,209
it's said that Bao Xijie liked seafood,

125
00:07:17,210 --> 00:07:20,000
especially the dishes
at Haitian Grand Hotel.

126
00:07:20,090 --> 00:07:22,089
He celebrated his birthday there
every year,

127
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:23,849
so it was expected
he'd choose there again

128
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:25,250
this year.

129
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:29,209
Have you found the source of the money?

130
00:07:29,210 --> 00:07:30,320
We're looking into it.

131
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:35,490
Any thoughts, Mochou?

132
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,170
Well.

133
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:41,459
Bringing one million in cash
to celebrate his own birthday

134
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:43,880
is suspicious in itself.

135
00:07:50,060 --> 00:07:51,290
The results are in.

136
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,459
We traced the serial numbers
of the money.

137
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:55,899
At 4:30 PM on March 30,
the day when Bao Xijie was murdered,

138
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:58,939
someone withdrew
one million in cash from bank

139
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:00,080
on Chengjiao Street.

140
00:08:00,090 --> 00:08:03,000
The person who withdrew it
was Ning Zhiyuan.

141
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:10,850
Mr. Ning, Ning Zhiyuan.

142
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:12,729
Yes, I am.

143
00:08:12,730 --> 00:08:14,810
CEO of Tianci Group.

144
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,560
Do you know Bao Xijie?

145
00:08:18,850 --> 00:08:21,290
Yes, we were business partners.

146
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:26,139
At 4:30 PM on March 30,

147
00:08:26,140 --> 00:08:27,520
where were you?

148
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:29,059
Chengjiao Street.

149
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:31,619
I withdrew one million cash from a bank.

150
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:41,550
(Ning Jing, Zeng Xiang, Bao Xijie,
Li Guangrong, Luo Yifei, Ning Zhiyuan)

151
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:59,040
You seem well-prepared.

152
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,160
The tragedy of Mr. Bao
and his family is big news.

153
00:09:02,290 --> 00:09:03,400
Everyone knows.

154
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:06,760
Mr. Bao and I were strictly
business partners.

155
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:08,049
We weren't close.

156
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,610
We met for tea a few times.

157
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,680
A while back, Mr. Bao said
he had some difficulties in business

158
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,979
and urgently needed cash,

159
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:15,330
so he came to me.

160
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:19,330
This is the IOU he signed.

161
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:26,610
Mr. Bao had a bad reputation,

162
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:29,240
and I was worried it might affect
my company,

163
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,400
so I didn't transfer the money
from the company account.

164
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,520
I withdrew cash instead.

165
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:37,400
Also, I didn't know

166
00:09:37,570 --> 00:09:39,880
March 30 was his birthday.

167
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,760
He probably reserved the hotel
in advance,

168
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,480
picked up the money,
and went straight there.

169
00:09:47,530 --> 00:09:49,920
I feel like you already knew
what I was going to ask,

170
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,520
and you had your answers ready.

171
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:57,090
I know a thing or two about
how interrogations work.

172
00:10:14,410 --> 00:10:15,520
Officer Li.

173
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:17,160
Hi, Officer Li.

174
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:19,160
May I have a word with you?

175
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:21,120
Sure.

176
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,250
Coffee.

177
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,570
Thank you, Officer Li.

178
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:32,289
You saved me last time.

179
00:10:32,290 --> 00:10:34,040
I haven't had a chance to thank you.

180
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:35,809
It's my duty.

181
00:10:35,810 --> 00:10:36,970
You don't have to do that.

182
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:40,040
Officer Li,

183
00:10:42,170 --> 00:10:44,040
Zhiyuan and you...

184
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:47,289
I don't know how much you know
about our past,

185
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:49,899
but I've always seen him
as a younger brother.

186
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,769
Right.

187
00:10:50,770 --> 00:10:52,280
Is it because of his sister?

188
00:10:52,410 --> 00:10:55,400
Zhiyuan told me you two
used to work together.

189
00:10:57,770 --> 00:10:59,160
Yes, we were colleagues.

190
00:10:59,570 --> 00:11:00,730
Mochou,

191
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:03,809
you've known Zhiyuan for a long time.

192
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:07,259
Do you know what he likes or dislikes?

193
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:09,370
Could you please tell me?

194
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:11,929
You two are a couple now.

195
00:11:11,930 --> 00:11:13,570
It's better

196
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:15,880
if you ask him directly.

197
00:11:16,170 --> 00:11:18,569
Mochou, you're an expert in psychology.

198
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:22,090
Could you teach me a little
if you have time?

199
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:24,760
That way, I can figure him out better.

200
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:29,730
You want to study psychology
just to figure Zhiyuan out?

201
00:11:30,170 --> 00:11:31,370
Isn't that silly?

202
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:34,379
No, you're cute.

203
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:36,259
I just feel like

204
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:38,800
he's hiding a lot from me.

205
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:43,090
What exactly is he hiding from you?

206
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,330
Zhiyuan.

207
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:50,160
We should get going.

208
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,970
Mochou, let's meet up
when you have time.

209
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:56,400
See you next time.

210
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:57,730
Bye-bye.

211
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,970
It's almost done.

212
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:12,739
Here you go.

213
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:15,019
Hurry and try them. Quick.

214
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:15,689
It's so hot.

215
00:12:15,690 --> 00:12:16,689
Look at what happened.

216
00:12:16,690 --> 00:12:18,330
A criminal actually worked here,

217
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,330
yet you still came here to eat.

218
00:12:20,530 --> 00:12:21,619
I was so blind.

219
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,920
I didn't even realize it.

220
00:12:23,930 --> 00:12:25,289
Sir, please don't say that.

221
00:12:25,290 --> 00:12:28,250
If you could've discovered him,
why would the police be needed?

222
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:30,979
Losing a barbecue cook is no big deal.

223
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:32,499
We can grill the skewers ourselves.

224
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:34,019
It's called the self-service barbecue.

225
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:35,440
- Right.
- That's the trend now.

226
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:35,899
All right.

227
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:38,929
You guys must eat your fill.
It's on the house.

228
00:12:38,930 --> 00:12:39,589
Here, have one.

229
00:12:39,589 --> 00:12:41,499
- All right.
- My skewers taste just as good as his.

230
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,570
- Absolutely.
- Sure, thank you.

231
00:12:45,530 --> 00:12:46,259
How does it taste?

232
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:47,490
Good.

233
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:52,920
Where's Mochou?

234
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,499
Oh yeah.

235
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,640
Where's Ms. Li?

236
00:12:55,770 --> 00:12:57,979
I saw her

237
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,450
walking toward the beach just now.

238
00:13:00,260 --> 00:13:02,769
She's been feeling down lately.

239
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:04,520
Looks like something's on her mind.

240
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:14,019
I've been looking for her
for the past year.

241
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:16,449
I sent her countless messages,
but she didn't reply to any of them.

242
00:13:16,450 --> 00:13:17,449
She never came home either.

243
00:13:17,449 --> 00:13:19,240
It's like she's a completely
different person.

244
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:21,000
I don't understand why
she became like this.

245
00:13:24,690 --> 00:13:25,099
Ning Jing,

246
00:13:25,100 --> 00:13:27,070
(Tomb of My Sister, Ning Jing)

247
00:13:27,170 --> 00:13:29,280
I'll definitely find out the truth.

248
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:46,690
It's late now. Why are you here alone?

249
00:13:49,140 --> 00:13:50,490
What are you doing here?

250
00:13:53,140 --> 00:13:55,000
About what happened before, I apologize.

251
00:13:55,530 --> 00:14:00,640
I shouldn't have acted on my own accord
and caused trouble for you and the squad.

252
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:07,280
But most importantly,

253
00:14:10,170 --> 00:14:11,640
thank you for saving my life.

254
00:14:12,930 --> 00:14:14,090
Well.

255
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:14,859
We're friends.

256
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:16,330
There's no need to thank me.

257
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:20,120
Friends?

258
00:14:21,050 --> 00:14:24,730
We went through life-and-death situations
together. Doesn't that make us friends?

259
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:33,570
Stop calling me Captain Ding
from now on.

260
00:14:33,620 --> 00:14:34,760
It sounds like a stranger.

261
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:39,570
What should I call you then?

262
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,120
Ding Wei.

263
00:14:45,770 --> 00:14:46,920
I must say,

264
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:50,289
exposing yourself

265
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:54,250
as bait was indeed effective.

266
00:14:56,690 --> 00:15:00,169
But you also put yourself in danger.

267
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:03,120
That's more serious
than going against regulations.

268
00:15:06,220 --> 00:15:08,690
To get close to you,

269
00:15:09,410 --> 00:15:12,450
