292
00:16:12,650 --> 00:16:16,569
But she told me cops mustn't
be afraid of trouble.

293
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:20,040
What she appreciated most about me was
that I questioned everything.

294
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,649
She told me not to hold back

295
