and dig for doubts,
she would be there to resolve them.

296
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:25,570
She's a good cop.

297
00:16:26,570 --> 00:16:27,730
Yes.

298
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,450
She was a good cop.

299
00:16:35,260 --> 00:16:36,690
She...

300
00:16:37,050 --> 00:16:38,160
She's gone.

301
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:45,370
One time, we went out on an operation

302
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:48,730
to meet someone
who claimed to be an informant.

303
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:53,330
We didn't expect it to be a trap.

304
00:16:55,530 --> 00:16:56,649
Back then,

305
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:57,880
I blindly believed

306
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:01,210
