was the key to everything.

307
00:17:01,570 --> 00:17:02,769
I didn't realize

308
00:17:02,770 --> 00:17:04,859
that Ning Jing was already in danger.

309
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:06,560
Because of my mistake,

310
00:17:08,210 --> 00:17:09,450
she died.

311
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:17,249
Also, Zeng Xiang,
the so-called informant,

312
00:17:17,250 --> 00:17:18,730
also died accidentally.

313
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:22,760
I followed the clue Zeng Xiang
left behind, which led me to Baizhou.

314
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:26,170
Also, Li Guangrong tried to
kill me twice.

315
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:28,449
I suspect someone behind him

316
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,890
is connected to the person
who killed Ning Jing.

317
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:33,930
Trust your instinct

318
00:17:34,380 --> 00:17:35,840
and judgment.

319
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:38,169
