339
00:19:05,170 --> 00:19:06,410
Batong Port.

340
00:19:12,690 --> 00:19:13,650
Look.

341
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:14,249
Over there.

342
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:15,250
Okay.

343
00:19:15,410 --> 00:19:16,600
Let's go.

344
00:19:25,010 --> 00:19:26,250
