345
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:29,490
All right,

346
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,059
I won't come any closer.

347
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,280
We're the police.

348
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,760
You can talk to us
