359
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:07,360
I'm not afraid to die.

360
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:09,320
Don't move.

361
00:20:09,650 --> 00:20:10,840
I'm not moving.

362
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:13,450
