387
00:21:10,650 --> 00:21:12,520
There's no sign of her now.

388
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:13,929
That woman is desperate

389
00:21:13,930 --> 00:21:14,819
and drinks a little.

390
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:16,080
She almost

