413
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:02,360
She's probably already fled
with the money by now.

414
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:05,130
You're still drinking here so casually.

415
00:22:05,410 --> 00:22:07,040
Keep investigating. Go on!

416
00:22:07,490 --> 00:22:08,650
Yes, madam.

417
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:14,760
Oh, my. Young people these days.

418
00:22:20,300 --> 00:22:22,280
January, 2018.

419
00:22:22,730 --> 00:22:23,899
You're eating instant noodles?

420
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,080
Ms. Li,

421
