Captain Ding's case again?

427
00:22:36,930 --> 00:22:40,539
No, I just need to verify some details

428
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:41,760
and review the case.

429
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:44,539
All right.

430
00:22:44,540 --> 00:22:45,690
Thank you.

431
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:47,720
Don't eat too much junk food.
It's unhealthy.

